snippet.title: Table of Tales: The Crooked Crown - E3 2018 Teaser Trailer | PS VR
snippet.description:
Tin Man Games introduces Table of Tales: The Crooked Crown, the RPG adventure that brings tabletop gaming to life in PS VR! Determine the fate of a party of scoundrels as you journey the lands of the Crown Islands, accompanied by Arbitrix, your unconventional Game Master...
